de179ddc-66a6-4ace-94f1-9131f2c70871	Project: ACTIVITI Workflow Migration v5 → v6 Summary Migration of an enterprise workflow engine from Activiti V5 to Activiti V6 as part of a broader initiative to digitalize and track banking products, particularly loan lifecycle processes. The work involved analyzing legacy BPMN workflows, understanding Activiti’s internal execution model (async jobs, activity types, gateway semantics), refactoring BPMN models for compatibility, and implementing migration scripts to preserve process definitions and runtime data. The goal was to modernize the workflow platform while ensuring continuity of critical banking operations.	{"loc": {"lines": {"to": 1, "from": 1}}, "source": "blob", "file_id": "1SWrYdBhBmQs8dtzu0061-QtT-d0doOt2", "blobType": "text/plain", "file_title": "activiti-migration.txt"}	[0.03401827,0.044130553,0.06994715,-0.032294057,-0.01894305,0.01620528,0.015401423,0.040938426,-0.016706234,-0.051679812,0.008801645,-0.046973173,-0.05536124,-0.03392507,0.022379829,0.092175536,0.024371995,-0.01882655,-0.022927383,0.021517722,0.08690969,-0.022344878,0.0071939323,0.033552267,-0.027237916,-0.051307008,-0.09590356,0.0015159684,-0.031664953,-0.08471947,0.040682122,-0.034204673,2.1275071e-05,0.065659925,0.009937529,0.0066289026,-0.021960424,0.015098521,0.022018675,0.030663043,-7.0765214e-05,-0.028566027,-0.006524052,0.040425822,-0.021610921,0.018640148,0.0061104735,0.0003859093,0.07106557,0.02006146,0.035579383,-0.044666454,0.028449526,-0.0128733525,-0.0057056327,-0.013281106,0.083507866,-0.004313447,-0.06430851,0.01505192,-0.00018876791,-0.00883077,0.04648387,-0.017882893,-0.012943253,0.0029139793,-0.05866987,0.01757999,0.01745184,-0.03511338,-0.022822531,0.020667264,0.007852162,-0.0031193122,-0.030057238,0.030732945,-0.0077181864,-0.00015545593,0.014084962,0.024069091,-0.001692176,-0.044643156,0.0024974886,-0.017090686,-0.0031076623,0.019059552,-0.020317761,-0.041963633,-0.046949875,-0.010921962,0.044666454,0.038515206,-0.006780354,0