9074cbae-a2f2-491c-8d1f-cb99eaf69654	Role & Responsibilities - Designed the migration strategy from Activiti V5 to V6, including compatibility analysis and execution planning. - Analyzed legacy BPMN models used for loan lifecycle orchestration and identified breaking changes related to async behavior and gateway semantics. - Studied Activiti’s internal architecture (job executor, async continuations, service/user tasks, call activities, gateway types). - Refactored BPMN XML models to align with Activiti V6 execution rules and ensure correct behavior in loan processing workflows. - Implemented and validated migration scripts to preserve process definitions, runtime instances, and historical workflow data. - Collaborated with internal technical teams to test, validate, and deploy the upgraded workflow engine with minimal operational disruption. - Provided guidance and technical support throughout the migration to ensure smooth adoption.	{"loc": {"lines": {"to": 1, "from": 1}}, "source": "blob", "file_id": "1SWrYdBhBmQs8dtzu0061-QtT-d0doOt2", "blobType": "text/plain", "file_title": "activiti-migration.txt"}	[0.01490352,0.04288415,0.089518525,-0.03253448,-0.017192623,0.0032388368,-0.011701211,0.025545413,-0.012036053,-0.04040023,0.021198552,-0.028565079,-0.031657804,-0.00026939574,0.0067333714,0.089421116,0.0059967185,0.00074083824,-0.03682046,0.03341116,0.05016544,-0.01468435,0.018264117,0.030026209,-0.009801743,-0.039474845,-0.06453321,0.015682789,-0.02586199,-0.07851135,0.04393129,-0.018519815,-0.00594497,0.055230692,-0.00655073,-0.022050878,-0.008967682,0.003744144,0.009978296,-0.0059693223,-0.02247704,-0.014988752,-0.015768021,0.046902254,-0.027006542,0.0025265364,0.01704651,0.0001901561,0.046342153,0.0050195884,0.033849496,-0.054597534,0.063072085,0.030099265,0.004639086,-0.009217291,0.09049261,-0.0075430805,-0.062244114,0.0064472333,-0.020760214,-0.026641259,0.021295961,-0.027030895,-0.0051657013,-0.013637207,-0.07821912,-0.006508114,0.0077074575,-0.031682156,-0.