e1140c65-e839-4e32-8f85-ed95808046a1	Project: Workflow Engines PoC (Palmyra R&D) Summary A large-scale proof‑of‑concept conducted within Palmyra R&D to compare multiple BPM engines (Camunda, Flowable, Activiti, jBPM) and determine the most suitable workflow engine for long‑term adoption in the enterprise framework. The study included performance benchmarks, stress tests, licensing evaluation, and backward compatibility analysis with the existing Activiti‑based workflow. A pluggable, adapter‑based architecture was designed to allow seamless switching between engines with minimal downtime. The project concluded with strategic recommendations and technical documentation that led to the adoption of Camunda.	{"loc": {"lines": {"to": 1, "from": 1}}, "source": "blob", "file_id": "1CqcqTB33HGhdzEJPS1_ErQKb8j6QcT6T", "blobType": "text/plain", "file_title": "workflow-engines-poc.txt"}	[0.010646065,0.036942426,0.09531867,-0.016835338,0.0153540345,-0.024125928,-0.04735019,0.007541768,0.03761223,-0.022232436,0.022477172,-0.04142498,-0.04701529,-0.021369414,0.043382876,0.04204326,0.008475633,-0.048947424,-0.019256948,0.027049892,0.060488712,-0.010092186,-0.019115258,0.031609733,0.011103337,-0.05142056,-0.06770202,0.012874461,-0.005046093,-0.08908431,0.040626362,-0.036375664,-0.015341153,0.012822937,-0.0026180432,-0.00030572014,0.00030793404,0.0057674237,-0.013099876,0.011792465,-0.035216384,-0.024022881,-0.0024683026,0.02473133,-0.014928964,0.027333273,-0.0062246956,0.04232664,0.055954635,-0.0027822747,-0.006462992,-0.0026357544,0.035499763,-0.031815827,0.014413728,-0.031352114,0.0149804875,-0.0001445076,-0.02473133,-0.010768433,0.0146069415,-0.024203213,0.04961723,0.0075095654,-0.056779012,0.027410557,-0.06801116,0.016332982,0.014697108,0.008900703,0.002843459,0.05062194,-0.010485053,-0.005084736,0.0014402458,-0.012790735,0.025298089,0.032485634,-0.03127483,0.019797945,-0.0073292325,-0.006060464,0.015135059,-0.03745766,-0.00080223865,-0.009892532,0.0038674904,-0.034134388,-0.028