8eadacfb-056a-4179-87a9-fca5da8d0149	to guide engine selection. Technical Contributions - Designed a pluggable workflow engine layer using adapter and strategy patterns to abstract engine‑specific logic. - Implemented integration prototypes for Camunda, Flowable, Activiti, and jBPM, validating execution semantics and API compatibility. - Built automated performance and stress‑testing suites to measure throughput, latency, job execution behavior, and database interaction patterns. - Developed CI/CD pipelines to automate build, test, and deployment workflows for each engine integration. - Created flexible packaging options supporting standalone deployments, enterprise integration, and Spring Boot starter modules. - Delivered technical documentation, architectural diagrams, and migration guidelines for future adoption. - Facilitated workshops and presentations to align stakeholders	{"loc": {"lines": {"to": 1, "from": 1}}, "source": "blob", "file_id": "1CqcqTB33HGhdzEJPS1_ErQKb8j6QcT6T", "blobType": "text/plain", "file_title": "workflow-engines-poc.txt"}	[0.018833496,0.018709265,0.0866142,-0.041915707,0.0065407883,-0.022138054,-0.046164427,0.022001399,-0.016299173,-0.006068709,0.029591944,-0.017976297,-0.028225396,-0.01049135,0.016460674,0.061420053,-0.01128022,-0.0537177,-0.0065718465,0.035356283,0.052872926,-0.018671995,0.033120118,0.041915707,0.004546873,-0.015243205,-0.025815306,0.050313756,-0.03580352,-0.091235615,0.033269197,-0.031852957,0.004009572,0.0057891877,0.030834258,-0.02941802,0.038039684,0.008211702,-0.00025642157,0.014895357,-0.01826203,-0.00081449276,0.0113423355,0.04827636,-0.010006847,0.0037114162,-0.010329849,0.013976044,0.021442357,0.0058419863,0.007845219,-0.0067022895,0.06494823,0.01171503,0.016771253,-0.0024271728,0.017094254,-0.040101927,-0.03635014,0.023877295,-0.000778388,-0.019106805,0.030337332,0.053767394,-0.047456432,-0.020423658,-0.029914945,-0.010864045,-0.011758512,-0.0021880274,0.027231544,0.06569362,-0.01222438,-0.02827509,0.01336730