c4533e4e-0837-4b38-92a2-50d3d88bd235	on engine selection. Achievements & Impact - Successfully delivered a comprehensive comparative study of BPM engines, documenting strengths, weaknesses, and enterprise adoption constraints. - Enabled seamless switching between workflow engines through an adapter‑based architecture, reducing migration risk and downtime. - Achieved measurable performance improvements with Camunda, including faster database exchanges and improved scalability under stress tests. - Established best practices for pluggable workflow engine integration following SOLID and clean architecture principles. - Improved deployment reliability by optimizing CI/CD pipelines and supporting multiple deployment strategies. - Ensured smooth adoption through knowledge‑transfer sessions and detailed documentation for developers, architects, and analysts. - Provided a clear technical foundation that guided the strategic decision to adopt Camunda within Palmyra	{"loc": {"lines": {"to": 1, "from": 1}}, "source": "blob", "file_id": "1CqcqTB33HGhdzEJPS1_ErQKb8j6QcT6T", "blobType": "text/plain", "file_title": "workflow-engines-poc.txt"}	[0.022070527,0.024349118,0.1266472,-0.018705633,0.0128833065,-0.012326906,-0.06411846,0.018533414,0.010445745,-0.019725699,0.039477896,-0.047532447,-0.028349897,-0.016493281,0.038524065,0.07673019,-0.006895384,-0.027608031,-0.010704073,0.013267487,0.07164311,-0.018798366,0.018626148,0.05407677,0.005140075,-0.016956948,-0.03878902,0.029224241,-0.048380293,-0.085102685,0.036960848,-0.022746157,0.010942531,0.0075113983,-0.0047260867,0.017473605,0.009902593,0.009829731,-0.018361196,0.0052593034,-0.029012278,0.0019076567,-0.003176116,0.060250156,-0.010286774,-0.0037987537,0.005795832,0.006269434,0.049016178,0.014015977,-0.0016079294,0.00888915,0.059190348,-0.035848048,0.02489227,-0.01116774,0.031211382,-0.012783949,-0.05606391,-0.025355937,-0.010392754,-0.029250735,0.040034294,0.029939612,-0.05095033,0.0050042868,-0.054368217,0.009736998,-0.006256