75913fcd-ab4c-4855-b2c7-721fab08d115	DevOps & Deployment - GitLab CI/CD: automated pipelines, testing, continuous deployment. - Docker: containerization, image optimization, environment consistency. - Kubernetes: orchestration, scaling, deployments, services. Build & Testing - Maven: build automation, dependency management, modular packaging. - JUnit: unit and integration testing for engine validation. Documentation & Collaboration - Confluence: technical and functional documentation. - PowerPoint: comparative presentations and workshops. - JIRA: issue tracking, sprint planning, Agile workflow. Domains & Topics - BPMN workflow engines - Workflow engine migration - Pluggable architecture design - Adapter and strategy patterns - Performance benchmarking - Stress and resilience testing - Licensing and cost analysis - Enterprise workflow orchestration - CI/CD automation - Containerized deployments - Kubernetes orchestration - Backward compatibility strategies - Technical documentation and knowledge transfer	{"loc": {"lines": {"to": 1, "from": 1}}, "source": "blob", "file_id": "1CqcqTB33HGhdzEJPS1_ErQKb8j6QcT6T", "blobType": "text/plain", "file_title": "workflow-engines-poc.txt"}	[0.0011412108,0.030622233,0.079627715,-0.018234598,0.0053607486,-0.001383544,-0.03513133,0.034834027,-0.020439597,-0.01958485,0.005620889,-0.011340879,-0.0066583534,-0.018271761,0.007091921,0.0599066,-0.018445188,-0.02273131,-0.013514909,0.013948476,0.06803289,-0.007519294,0.012796426,0.03785661,-0.01880443,-0.008863352,-0.049748737,0.059708398,-0.0015422604,-0.06833019,0.066050865,-0.031315938,-0.023598444,0.03785661,0.03959088,0.034239423,0.0077113025,0.036692172,-0.009290726,0.02675729,-0.034784477,0.0024930113,-0.032108746,0.012486735,-0.016995834,-0.0013440583,-0.025122123,-0.004982926,0.0102445735,-0.007946667,-0.016698532,-0.00018291116,0.052721772,-0.005205903,0.019002631,0.01838325,0.01528634,-0.007413999,-0.02461423,-0.014902324,0.045066215,-0.031291164,0.039863408,0.0032982077,-0.0246