52b5a6db-87a1-478f-8936-ea9fe8e3cbea	Project: Palmyra Vulnerabilities Reference Platform Summary Design and development of a centralized vulnerabilities reference platform integrated into the Palmyra ecosystem. The platform provides visibility into security risks related to framework dependencies and supports development and QA teams in identifying, tracking, and understanding vulnerabilities over time. It consolidates vulnerability data, offers historical evolution insights, and provides actionable remediation strategies. The solution integrates seamlessly with Palmyra’s existing data structures and workflows, strengthening the overall security posture of the framework by embedding vulnerability tracking directly into its core architecture. Business Context As Palmyra evolved, dependency complexity and security requirements increased. Teams needed a unified, reliable source of truth for vulnerability tracking, risk assessment, and remediation guidance. Existing tools (Maven, SonarQube) provided raw data but lacked contex	{"loc": {"lines": {"to": 1, "from": 1}}, "source": "blob", "file_id": "1JZzCJaBsmXqegSR66xvJddbT-AYy8ziZ", "blobType": "text/plain", "file_title": "palmyra-vulnerabilities-referance.txt"}	[-0.003058717,0.03468352,0.105580725,0.021804715,-0.010016142,0.0032499863,-0.01338886,0.0068283184,0.023385875,0.007434005,0.018004829,-0.022952331,-0.014995523,-0.037769336,0.0039560893,0.029965544,0.06936704,0.03799886,-0.058043897,0.06447055,0.048480425,0.015314305,-0.030832632,-0.009665482,-0.012897935,-0.03878944,-0.020886622,0.015492824,0.041288693,-0.016563931,0.05472856,-0.032031253,0.011680187,0.049168993,-0.011935213,0.020465828,-0.014000922,-0.024074445,-0.035040557,0.064980604,0.0055468134,-0.002188441,-0.029302476,0.0551366,0.004198364,-0.0042748717,-0.0055818795,0.06758186,0.007740036,-0.012292248,-0.0010376367,-0.06268537,0.044757046,-0.0005208107,-0.032745328,-0.04205377,-0.01958599,0.05365745,-0.05100518,0.015990125,-0.010347676,-0.021116145,0.01