efa5b071-1792-4321-a04f-3bd69f5d3827	ing workflows. Technical Contributions - Built Spring Boot microservices powering the vulnerability tracking, analysis, and reporting features. - Integrated SonarQube APIs and Maven dependency scanning to automate vulnerability ingestion. - Designed data models to store vulnerability metadata, historical snapshots, severity evolution, and remediation notes. - Implemented REST APIs for querying vulnerabilities, filtering by module, severity, or timeframe. - Packaged services into Docker images and deployed them on Kubernetes clusters for scalability and resilience. - Authored documentation and analysis reports in Confluence to support QA and development teams. Achievements & Impact - Delivered a centralized vulnerabilities reference platform improving developer and QA efficiency. - Enabled proactive detection of dependency risks through automated Maven and SonarQube integration. - Provided historical vulnerability analysis, helping teams understand root causes and long‑term impact. - De	{"loc": {"lines": {"to": 1, "from": 1}}, "source": "blob", "file_id": "1JZzCJaBsmXqegSR66xvJddbT-AYy8ziZ", "blobType": "text/plain", "file_title": "palmyra-vulnerabilities-referance.txt"}	[0.030971587,0.040253446,0.13283156,-0.033039566,0.009594459,-0.010892957,-0.03724766,0.030418523,-0.0025128345,-0.0119810505,0.013201398,0.004746131,-0.041768357,-0.009263823,-0.015161169,0.05636444,0.011265674,-0.012065212,-0.04212905,0.047996342,0.046216916,0.00049445126,0.031428464,0.008115614,0.01144001,-0.0022949153,-0.08122828,0.03397737,0.007929255,-0.033472396,-0.008770875,-0.026402796,-0.033616677,0.04633715,0.0017538742,0.013201398,-0.029120024,-0.017373424,-0.0071958443,0.019958397,0.008386134,0.008289949,0.014764406,0.07492816,-0.018299205,-0.013586138,-0.04323518,0.0035107543,-0.007520469,0.018575737,-0.0018981518,-0.044605818,0.052036114,0.0018981518,0.006672838,-0.029120024,0.013045098,0.008452262,-0.053623166,0.030418523,0.009738737,-0.039532054,0