912fd37c-bfac-4f7c-ac3a-7acb3f419c86	Project: Palmyra Framework – Transversal Enterprise Backbone Summary Long-term contribution to the evolution and maintenance of the Palmyra framework, a transversal enterprise platform used across numerous client projects and business domains. The framework provides shared services, reusable components, and standardized integration patterns that ensure consistency, interoperability, and reliability across heterogeneous applications. The work involved enhancing core modules, supporting cross‑cutting requirements, maintaining compatibility with diverse deployment environments, and ensuring stable behavior across multiple database engines and messaging systems. This project played a central role in enabling teams to deliver consistent, high‑quality solutions while reducing duplication, improving maintainability, and supporting long‑term scalability across the Palmyra and Veggo ecosystems. Business Context Palmyra serves as the foundational layer for many enterprise applications used by cl	{"loc": {"lines": {"to": 1, "from": 1}}, "source": "blob", "file_id": "19_b6XyPDhcrEru32o2BPP4frf4HQYoQU", "blobType": "text/plain", "file_title": "palmyra-framework.txt"}	[-0.031124137,0.0118888235,0.102334864,0.028000861,0.033975825,-0.005472525,-0.031151297,0.032319132,0.02370975,0.0060734167,0.044676445,-0.050923,-0.021428399,-0.03188459,0.029684715,0.073383436,0.048723128,0.0154941715,-0.0335956,0.043155547,0.05037982,-0.0048750285,-0.009003187,0.0020114586,-0.015154685,-0.031748794,-0.051574815,0.051031638,0.0156028075,-0.07805478,0.03745217,-0.020735845,0.026113315,0.028055178,-0.005424997,-0.001482708,0.011657972,0.0046238084,0.0067863385,0.048125632,-0.0018043716,-0.053829007,-0.024375143,0.0067591798,0.023030777,0.0027634215,0.00072353095,0.046794843,0.03614854,0.0013044776,-0.006188842,-0.056870807,0.045409735,-0.018902618,-0.0290329,-0.0067116516,0.027702112,0.03307958,-0.051276065,0.011427121,-0.027118195,-0.033052422,0.027607055,-0.00