ec25238e-46f5-4f84-a239-e355a709b3b2	RM mappings, caching strategies, and transactional boundaries. - Ensured deployment portability across multiple application servers and environments. - Implemented multithreading and concurrency mechanisms to support high‑volume transactional workloads. - Delivered extensive unit test coverage to ensure long‑term stability of framework modules. - Provided technical support to client teams integrating Palmyra into their solutions. Achievements & Impact - Delivered consistent support for multiple deployment environments and database engines across all client projects. - Ensured robust persistence, caching, and transactional concurrency mechanisms for enterprise‑grade performance. - Enhanced data integration pipelines enabling interoperability across diverse client systems. - Improved reliability of job scheduling and messaging systems used in mission‑critical workflows. - Strengthened the Palmyra framework by maintaining and enhancing transversal modules across a wide technology stack. -	{"loc": {"lines": {"to": 1, "from": 1}}, "source": "blob", "file_id": "19_b6XyPDhcrEru32o2BPP4frf4HQYoQU", "blobType": "text/plain", "file_title": "palmyra-framework.txt"}	[-0.014011702,0.022915956,0.1123098,0.021389125,0.01645733,0.0066342773,-0.00937041,0.012363266,0.026834367,-0.00080732803,0.03313085,-0.022010667,0.002656751,-0.014335983,0.01445759,0.04169731,0.018835401,0.04048125,-0.03242824,0.041886475,0.05539824,-0.009505527,-0.009296095,-0.010336501,-0.0054080845,-0.03542785,-0.030482544,0.02271328,-0.011018845,-0.081935346,0.041805405,-0.016619472,0.0033390953,-0.0031566864,0.0038643652,0.019159684,0.03342811,0.0153223425,-0.004354167,0.02049735,-0.0035367047,-0.03467119,-0.032725498,0.03631963,-0.0047088503,0.015403413,-0.00070767873,0.02861792,0.045940004,0.006931536,-0.011930889,-0.019402897,0.056695372,0.009654157,0.0041346005,0.008242177,0.041183863,0.035698086,-0.059343677,-0.014281937,-0.03234717,-0.033752393,0.019038077,-0.0044183