e2440991-a054-4ef2-b10d-75481a563e7b	Enabled teams to deliver consistent, standardized solutions while reducing development effort and duplication. Technologies Used Backend & Integration - Apache Camel: data integration (CSV, Excel, XML, JSON). - Spring Data: persistence, CRUD APIs. - Hibernate: ORM, caching. - MyBatis: ORM integration. - Spring Core: transactional support. - Java: multithreading, concurrency. Messaging - RabbitMQ, ActiveMQ, Apache Kafka, Amazon SQS. Scheduling - Quartz: job scheduling and task orchestration. Testing - JUnit: unit testing and regression validation. Deployment - IBM WebSphere, JBoss, WildFly, Tomcat. Databases - MSSQL, Oracle, PostgreSQL. Domains & Topics - Transversal framework engineering - Enterprise integration patterns - Messaging systems (distributed & cloud) - Data transformation pipelines - ORM and persistence optimization - Transactional concurrency - Multi‑environment deployment - Multi‑database compatibility - Standardization across client solutions - Long‑term framework evolut	{"loc": {"lines": {"to": 1, "from": 1}}, "source": "blob", "file_id": "19_b6XyPDhcrEru32o2BPP4frf4HQYoQU", "blobType": "text/plain", "file_title": "palmyra-framework.txt"}	[-0.0072888825,0.0050877533,0.12336387,-0.010389331,0.03592243,-0.0093265,-0.019734697,0.05327991,0.0048802183,-0.016087111,0.026388397,-0.012779128,-0.036073364,0.012873462,0.021986138,0.050739177,0.012917485,-0.009728991,-0.033130143,0.033759035,0.036274612,0.026086528,0.004980841,0.01942025,0.00017481291,-0.010345308,-0.07717788,0.05987072,-0.015282127,-0.09136573,0.029532867,-0.03141955,-0.013647002,0.015131192,0.024099221,0.016489603,0.035620563,0.03957002,0.017609036,0.01241437,-0.007798287,-0.01894229,0.007345483,0.014829323,-0.030086294,-0.009911371,-0.023797354,-0.032752804,0.01948314,0.02012461,-0.0037041863,-0.0477708,0.061732244,0.012634482,0.023344548,-0.006704011,0.013143887,0.04643754,-0.01989821,0.0046035047,-0.007968089,-0.043444004,0.017860593,0.024916785,-0.038