a4fbbc8d-8aa7-4e27-a871-64a244823dfc	Project: Palmyra/Veggo Chatbot Backend Summary Development of the backend for the Palmyra/Veggo chatbot, designed to provide AI‑driven assistance to users interacting with the Palmyra framework and Veggo platform. The solution consisted of Spring Boot microservices handling CRUD operations for conversation sessions and messages, integrated with a Python backend hosting fine‑tuned generative AI models. The main challenges included maintaining conversation context through session tracking and optimizing prompts to improve response quality, efficiency, and relevance. Business Context Palmyra and Veggo users needed an intelligent assistant capable of guiding them through documentation, framework usage, and business process design. The chatbot had to deliver contextual, accurate, and actionable responses while integrating seamlessly with existing platform ecosystems.	{"loc": {"lines": {"to": 1, "from": 1}}, "source": "blob", "file_id": "1gn5gyDJyBi9w_bV_agkWgEqY6y9g43gS", "blobType": "text/plain", "file_title": "veggo-ai-chatbot.txt"}	[-0.025234468,0.020583566,0.04911353,-0.019746404,-0.027905416,-0.01813852,0.0013969318,0.041512627,0.055757675,-0.0052987067,0.03622389,-0.0661757,-0.04023695,-0.03215767,-0.04390452,0.030775687,-0.00480704,-0.0026161326,-0.02934055,0.01672996,0.050389208,0.009248652,-0.012265095,0.0077736513,-0.004444934,-0.016251583,-0.0011768445,0.041300014,0.0022457214,-0.069683805,0.0031626136,-0.024716225,-0.026058342,-0.004258898,-0.012444486,-0.02669618,0.02413154,-0.02062343,0.015387843,0.047279745,-0.015653608,-0.035479743,0.02748019,0.037871636,0.023334242,0.032423433,0.0012474385,0.06479371,0.006614248,-0.011494373,-0.07026849,-0.041937854,0.011999329,0.013394599,-0.029792354,-0.0030247476,0.0057206103,0.024038522,-0.030988298,0.0326892,-0.026297532,-0.028118027,0.039705418,-0.007926467,-0.05517299,-0.018404286,-0.05105362,0.006159124,-0.03252974,-0.016304735,0.0062355315,0.010796738,-0.051106773,-0.04712028