2c3665e5-a167-4f72-8dcf-91421886ac25	This required a robust backend capable of managing conversation history, interacting with AI services, and ensuring consistent behavior across environments. Role & Responsibilities - Optimized AI prompts to improve efficiency, accuracy, and relevance of generative responses. - Developed Spring Boot microservices providing CRUD operations for chatbot sessions and messages. - Integrated the backend with a Python AI service hosting fine‑tuned generative models trained on Palmyra/Veggo documentation. - Implemented session tracking mechanisms to maintain conversation context across multi‑turn interactions. - Ensured seamless integration of the chatbot backend with the Palmyra framework and Veggo platform ecosystem.	{"loc": {"lines": {"to": 1, "from": 1}}, "source": "blob", "file_id": "1gn5gyDJyBi9w_bV_agkWgEqY6y9g43gS", "blobType": "text/plain", "file_title": "veggo-ai-chatbot.txt"}	[-0.0016576123,0.008168971,0.08729019,-0.008020912,-0.0008219665,-0.004203576,0.02034196,0.04416008,0.018964373,0.016260695,0.030358445,-0.03849523,-0.028993731,-0.008703269,-0.044391822,0.027217029,-0.027062533,-0.016711308,-0.02376662,-0.004760405,0.021513555,0.008201158,0.010055109,0.01995572,0.016080448,-0.013994754,-0.0028098943,0.042434875,-0.01588733,-0.06499128,0.006305364,-0.023097139,-0.03934496,0.019273365,-0.016106198,-0.036795776,0.02677929,-0.014290871,0.015784333,0.020638078,-0.018230516,-0.026045434,0.035637055,0.03857248,-0.0013357459,0.020097343,-0.017097548,0.025762193,-0.012069993,0.013428269,-0.07003815,-0.010705279,0.022195911,0.016312193,-0.016234946,0.01680143,0.010949898,0.0026891944,-0.015964577,0.042409126,-0.011780313,-0.031517167,0.029482968,0.01983985,-0.053404085,-0.021037193,-0.051627383,-0.014973228,-0.028041007,-0.00617018,0.024230108,0.018088896,-0.05057166,-0.049747683,-0.01622207,0.031594414,0.05386757,0.031877656,-0.0189,-0.06195286,-0.031079426,0.015320844,0.015153473,0.008864203,6.532884e-05,-0.018063147,-0.014020503