a8840723-c2c4-4366-ac76-d612135db110	Business Context Palmyra R&D needed to modernize its messaging capabilities to support distributed architectures, cloud deployments, and high‑throughput event‑driven workflows. Clients increasingly required integration with Kafka for distributed streaming and SQS for cloud‑native queuing. The existing framework lacked unified messaging support, making integration inconsistent and costly. This project introduced a standardized, extensible messaging layer that aligned with Palmyra’s architecture and enabled smooth adoption of both on‑premise and cloud messaging systems.	{"loc": {"lines": {"to": 1, "from": 1}}, "source": "blob", "file_id": "1g3SbHys3hE0ceOyg2K9cdYVjuPDgHoNN", "blobType": "text/plain", "file_title": "palmyra-messaging-ecosystem-enhancement.txt"}	[-0.018929405,0.0027375098,0.06400073,0.03578625,0.03600732,0.0025060736,-0.027122935,0.0017184998,0.043247472,-0.024442421,0.005789358,-0.037361395,-0.018542526,0.0070363497,0.035233565,0.02857373,0.04899538,0.026432082,-0.026653154,0.017450977,0.035482273,0.028062496,-0.03269122,-0.00038752603,-0.033326805,-0.022010615,-0.038162787,0.039433956,0.0044525554,-0.0892031,0.021623736,-0.029126413,-0.023793017,0.0062107793,0.0053472114,0.0089258365,-0.014991536,0.022963993,0.0033679141,0.03998664,-0.026556436,-0.047641303,0.00028454556,0.004677083,0.016953561,0.025768861,0.0055233794,0.056290798,0.037306126,0.018487258,-0.035316467,-0.038881272,0.04250135,-0.019537356,-0.03343734,-0.010466441,0.016469965,0.016566683,-0.019813698,0.013989798,0.009243629,-0.029983072,0.010956948,-0.01985515,-0.08201821,0.030812098,-0.04018008,-0.0028411378,-0.025672141,0.062232144,-0.0012236754,-0.0024473509,-0.025105642,0.00090329186,-0.00077202957,-0.003937869,-0.025976118,0.040097177,0.005875715,0.006956902,-0.0016882749,-0.032028,0.013589102,-0.011012216,-0.0012279933,-0.007813561,-0.027440729,0.045983255,-0.031447683,0.015254061,0.03036995,0.018418172,-0.01852871,0.018901771,0.030287048,-0.059