c135b1c3-f30c-4ff6-9523-dfb85ab0f2f5	Palmyra’s microservice architecture. - Designed Dockerized messaging services and deployed them on Kubernetes clusters for scalability and resilience. - Configured AWS infrastructure for SQS queues and ensured secure, reliable communication with Palmyra services. - Authored technical documentation, migration guidelines, and integration examples for client teams. Achievements & Impact - Enabled full support for Apache Kafka and Amazon SQS within the Palmyra framework. - Delivered a unified messaging layer allowing clients to switch between messaging systems without modifying business logic. - Improved scalability, resilience, and throughput of Palmyra‑based solutions through distributed messaging. - Provided documentation and guidelines that accelerated client adoption of messaging features. - Facilitated workshops and training sessions to ensure smooth onboarding for client technical teams. Technologies Used Messaging - Apache Kafka: distributed messaging, stream processing, high‑throu	{"loc": {"lines": {"to": 1, "from": 1}}, "source": "blob", "file_id": "1g3SbHys3hE0ceOyg2K9cdYVjuPDgHoNN", "blobType": "text/plain", "file_title": "palmyra-messaging-ecosystem-enhancement.txt"}	[-0.0012580022,-0.002911239,0.07161776,-0.00022573347,0.03066762,-0.019099783,-0.06051264,0.005176607,0.02496082,-0.016284943,0.01696616,-0.0477109,-0.021194847,-0.014935362,0.014177026,0.06154089,-0.0017271423,0.052749336,-0.02989643,0.019896679,0.055936918,0.028842472,-0.018277181,-0.004264033,-0.006792891,-0.016194971,-0.06112959,0.030282026,-0.01802012,-0.08164322,0.039073583,-0.019922385,-0.03164446,-0.011413598,0.0130845085,0.0040005436,0.0060313414,0.01056529,-0.024420988,0.041695625,-0.005761425,-0.05660528,-0.019279728,0.027685689,0.0069021424,0.026888793,0.030410556,0.053314872,0.018547097,0.011394319,-0.0035988824,0.0042158337,0.06251773,-0.024318162,-0.007833996,-0.008752996,0.015320957,0.044060603,-0.038739398,0.003316113,-0.035988826,-0.0546001