2f45ac5c-896e-4009-bc0c-35bc7ab3892b	Project: Veggo – Cloud‑Native BPMN Modeling Platform Summary Development of Spring Boot microservices for the Veggo platform, a cloud‑native solution enabling users to design and validate business processes through an intuitive BPMN.io modeler. The services were deployed on AWS Kubernetes using Docker images, providing scalable and resilient infrastructure. The project included BPMN validation, management of Veggo client project dependencies, and seamless interoperability with Palmyra project data structures. The result was a robust, extensible, and cloud‑ready process‑modeling ecosystem. Business Context Veggo aimed to offer a modern, user‑friendly platform for business process modeling, allowing clients to design workflows visually and validate them before execution. To support this, the platform required a backend capable of handling BPMN models, validating workflow correctness, and integrating with existing enterprise data structures from the Palmyra ecosystem. The solution needed	{"loc": {"lines": {"to": 1, "from": 1}}, "source": "blob", "file_id": "12z6ZOFD8YlvKd7PyD3jt81pSbH7NHyC7", "blobType": "text/plain", "file_title": "cloud-native-bpmn-plateform.txt"}	[-0.025731163,0.03714259,0.05412417,-0.031227378,-0.026692385,-0.008484629,-0.02069091,0.03351952,0.042269103,-0.023919629,0.02642127,-0.03494903,-0.018904025,-0.050772216,-0.013580335,0.078277946,-0.0015535128,-0.011781126,-0.030364743,0.0437972,0.051215857,-0.011978299,-0.018990288,0.031868193,-0.023278816,-0.012575982,-0.020888085,0.05111727,-0.00503409,-0.0763555,0.027875425,-0.046976622,-0.022625677,0.0031671019,-0.011818096,-0.040395953,0.005949099,0.006500569,-0.030734444,0.06763057,-0.05254678,-0.041086063,0.02204648,0.06570812,0.04515277,0.057969056,0.0073262337,0.04320568,-0.0031886678,0.0151454015,-0.029280288,-0.05195526,0.029896457,-0.00050872343,-0.028614827,0.0015881722,0.014578528,0.041135356,-0.04872654,0.020296564,0.0012469693,-0.040987473,0.03802987,0.