30706360-c984-4e86-9e3a-06f625dd8e36	to be scalable, cloud‑native, and maintainable to support a growing client base and evolving business needs. Role & Responsibilities - Developed Spring Boot microservices enabling Veggo users to design business processes using the BPMN.io modeler. - Deployed microservices on AWS Kubernetes clusters using Docker images to ensure scalability, resilience, and high availability. - Integrated BPMN validation mechanisms to guarantee correctness, compliance, and structural integrity of designed workflows. - Managed Veggo client project dependencies and ensured seamless integration with Palmyra project data structures. - Produced technical documentation and provided support to business users adopting BPMN‑based process modeling. Technical Contributions - Built modular Spring Boot microservices supporting BPMN model creation, validation, and persistence. - Integrated BPMN.io front‑end modeler with backend services for real‑time validation and workflow management. - Implemented BPMN validation l	{"loc": {"lines": {"to": 1, "from": 1}}, "source": "blob", "file_id": "12z6ZOFD8YlvKd7PyD3jt81pSbH7NHyC7", "blobType": "text/plain", "file_title": "cloud-native-bpmn-plateform.txt"}	[-0.01928274,0.050142493,0.08499645,-0.049282208,-0.017918568,-0.012369711,-0.02703762,0.030331293,0.0340674,-0.017500713,0.014465126,-0.023793105,-0.02073294,-0.028463239,-0.008289488,0.084799804,-0.006962187,-0.019639144,-0.03335459,0.04065475,0.050314553,0.0037883392,0.008522995,0.044194218,0.016050514,-0.015472893,-0.018938623,0.04471039,-0.0033213259,-0.08366914,0.007859345,-0.038516317,-0.035861716,0.0018142858,-0.009512327,-0.046553865,0.015730979,0.0038037016,-0.0068208543,0.056434885,-0.053780284,-0.027234256,0.0145880245,0.064595334,0.02410035,0.043555148,-0.001183664,0.043678045,-0.0036132091,0.02922521,-0.021236822,-0.041048024,0.06316971,0.025980694,-0.011632321,0.024604235,0.045668997,0.01424391,-0.07044529,0.039327446,0.013887505,-0.043776363,0.048102383,