44ddbbe7-4350-4d66-b8f4-cb732b9864f2	Project: Apache Camel in the Cloud – Scalability & Performance PoC Summary A proof‑of‑concept conducted within Palmyra R&D to evaluate the scalability, resilience, and performance of Apache Camel in cloud‑native environments. The project involved deploying Camel routes on Azure Kubernetes Services (AKS), containerizing integration pipelines, and testing large‑scale data routing under stress conditions. The study validated Camel’s ability to handle high‑throughput message flows, demonstrated horizontal scalability through dynamic pod scaling, and produced recommendations for adopting Camel in enterprise‑grade cloud architectures. Business Context As enterprise systems increasingly adopt cloud‑native architectures, integration frameworks like Apache Camel must demonstrate scalability, resilience, and operational efficiency in containerized environments. Palmyra R&D needed to assess whether Camel could support high‑volume routing workloads, dynamic scaling, and distributed processing in K	{"loc": {"lines": {"to": 1, "from": 1}}, "source": "blob", "file_id": "1Uvxv2u9G8cN4fqgb_HFSG8Bq6a1lPoH4", "blobType": "text/plain", "file_title": "poc-camel-cloud.txt"}	[-0.0032895089,-0.019755447,0.09820089,0.025997238,0.06283484,-0.03060807,0.007173766,0.005410982,0.05248499,0.013158035,0.0202337,-0.03818651,-0.0241946,-0.012219928,0.012986356,0.01653032,-0.027051842,-0.022404224,-0.010343713,0.040099513,0.033551153,0.014396584,-0.0015865059,0.020577058,-0.05219068,-0.055133764,-0.052337836,0.027885716,0.023127731,-0.10977702,0.034458604,-0.06200096,-0.047334593,-0.018394273,-0.02957799,-0.010662546,0.020638373,0.035415106,-0.0008223772,-0.012593945,-0.046181887,-0.024415331,0.02673301,0.03624898,0.02974967,0.007100189,0.04137485,-0.028842218,0.01958377,0.031368364,-0.01179686,0.0097980155,0.03833366,-0.025850084,0.0068917205,0.010122981,-0.010803569,0.009522102,-0.008191583,0.008694359,0.022183493,-0.06087278,-0.0012776355,0.004310391,-0.045568