7405e0ad-9773-4b63-9098-4058e569f50c	ubernetes. This PoC provided concrete insights into Camel’s behavior under load, its suitability for cloud deployments, and the operational strategies required for production‑grade adoption. Role & Responsibilities - Designed and executed a PoC to evaluate Apache Camel scalability in Kubernetes and cloud environments. - Configured Azure Kubernetes Services (AKS) clusters to deploy, monitor, and scale Camel routes under high‑load scenarios. - Implemented large‑scale data routing pipelines using Apache Camel components to test throughput and resilience. - Conducted stress and performance tests to benchmark Camel’s message handling capabilities in containerized environments. - Documented findings and provided recommendations for adopting Camel in enterprise cloud architectures. Technical Contributions - Built Camel routes applying enterprise integration patterns for large‑scale data routing. - Containerized Camel workloads using Docker and optimized images for Kubernetes deployments. - Co	{"loc": {"lines": {"to": 1, "from": 1}}, "source": "blob", "file_id": "1Uvxv2u9G8cN4fqgb_HFSG8Bq6a1lPoH4", "blobType": "text/plain", "file_title": "poc-camel-cloud.txt"}	[0.006088748,-0.02408134,0.058204506,0.0019869485,0.050447077,-0.03307615,-0.010523689,0.02182074,0.02905466,0.017192459,0.021761252,-0.012742646,-0.012457097,-0.019833792,0.010137007,0.0047115665,-0.047853336,-0.030196859,-0.028007647,0.04273724,0.02193972,0.016442891,0.0053064614,0.02596121,-0.027745893,-0.049542837,-0.039382033,0.007043554,0.015253102,-0.103083365,-0.0030101675,-0.057585813,-0.045378573,0.0023275258,-0.019405467,-0.018168086,0.018298963,0.033575863,0.0067758514,-0.0060114115,-0.034289736,-0.03295717,0.022011107,0.03624099,0.006460557,-0.0039947187,0.035646096,-0.04935247,0.017049685,0.01684742,-0.010904421,0.004458736,0.048924148,-0.015788507,0.010386863,0.0042148293,0.0016359607,0.024557257,-0.014087108,0.030101676,0.028983274,-0.066961356,0.006020335,0.0122191