7e5a3250-74a4-4afd-bb91-a368bd9e440d	nfigured AKS clusters, including autoscaling, monitoring, and resource allocation strategies. - Implemented performance and stress‑testing scenarios to measure throughput, latency, and resilience. - Designed monitoring and logging strategies to track message flow and performance metrics across distributed nodes. - Authored technical documentation and comparative analysis to guide future cloud‑native integration strategies. Achievements & Impact - Validated Apache Camel’s ability to handle high‑throughput routing in AKS with minimal latency. - Demonstrated horizontal scalability through dynamic pod scaling in Kubernetes. - Implemented monitoring and logging strategies enabling visibility into distributed message flows. - Produced documentation and analysis supporting enterprise adoption of Camel in cloud‑native architectures. - Delivered knowledge‑transfer sessions to R&D teams on Camel integration patterns and Kubernetes deployment strategies. Technologies Used Integration & Routing -	{"loc": {"lines": {"to": 1, "from": 1}}, "source": "blob", "file_id": "1Uvxv2u9G8cN4fqgb_HFSG8Bq6a1lPoH4", "blobType": "text/plain", "file_title": "poc-camel-cloud.txt"}	[0.019094184,-0.029639464,0.08215766,-0.01621597,0.045439012,-0.026259096,-0.014795237,0.0005036872,0.020465927,0.016044503,0.03728204,-0.011598584,-0.025891665,-0.0040846122,0.018861478,0.00552678,-0.065353796,-0.024679141,-0.019804552,0.04636984,0.038090385,0.014476797,0.019951524,0.009491977,-0.034342587,-0.03088873,-0.028341208,0.023442121,-0.012168103,-0.07049783,0.0013128017,-0.04930929,-0.034881487,-0.008653009,-0.021494735,0.00081141095,0.022180608,0.022903223,0.0036436946,-0.008365188,-0.018934963,-0.008377436,0.026406068,0.045806445,0.013999135,-0.003110919,0.02816974,-0.018726753,0.020441432,0.02211937,-0.008089614,0.0337302,0.05986682,0.0043203807,0.021457992,0.04333241,0.022143865,-0.0070975493,-0.0020805802,0.024238223,0.03336277,-0.05702535,0.02345437,0.019020697,-0.0